# Competency question: "What pronoun sets does PURRDF ship as values, and are they
# independent of sex?" Expected: the PronounSet value individuals (she/her,
# he/him, they/them, it/its, xe/xem, ze/hir, ey/em, any, ask). Sex/gender
# independent — any further set is expressed by filling the five form properties.

PREFIX purrdf: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/purrdf/>

SELECT ?pronounSet WHERE {
    ?pronounSet a purrdf:PronounSet .
}
ORDER BY ?pronounSet
